  "status": "Final",
  "summary": "A **Non-Fungible Token** (NFT) standard used to vest tokens ([ERC-20](./eip-20.md) or otherwise) over a vesting release curve. The following standard allows for the implementation of a standard API for NFT based contracts that hold and represent the vested and locked properties of any underlying token ([ERC-20](./eip-20.md) or otherwise) that is emitted to the NFT holder. This standard is an extension of the [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) token that provides basic functionality for creating vesting NFTs, claiming the tokens and reading vesting curve properties.",
  "title": "Transferable Vesting NFT"
